summary: This is a small modification to add a house and stable near WinterHold.
descriptionHtml: This is still in it\'s Alpha stage so there are many things that need to be fixed. This is my first modification for Skyrim, it adds a playerhome and a storage section to the bottom of WinterHouse. Located thirteen seconds away, is a \'Winter Stable Armory\' make sure you save before trying to gain access to the stable.
author: ThatBloodMage
